sentences: Isabel Rosales Pareja was born in Guayaquil on March 1, 1895, the daughter of cocoa farm owners Josefina Pareja Avilés and Carlos Rosales Llaguno.
Isabel Rosales Pareja died in Quito on April 8, 1961.
